item.title: CVE-2023-43086|2023-11-23T06:27:19.920Z -- dell -- dell%20command%20configure%20%28dcc%29
item.description: Dell Command | Configure, versions prior to 4.11.0, contains an improper access control vulnerability. A local malicious user could potentially modify files inside installation folder during application upgrade, leading to privilege escalation.
